review:
I got my dental implant from 
Dr Reddis dental kondapur. Dr.Obul reddy explained various options for missing tooth very clearly before starting the procedure and let me choose
from the available options. Unlike other dentists, he never recommends any complex procedures or medications if they are not really required. He suggests to go with simple alternatives without disturbing the natural teeth. The staff at the clinic deserves a big applaud. They

Overall, I had an excellent experience with Dr Reddis dental. Thank u Dr. Obul reddy and staff for your wonderful service.
